l Credit","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, what the new minimum rate of monthly deductions towards repayment of universal credit advance payments will be as a proportion of a claimant’s standard allowance once the maximum repayment period has been extended to 16 months, as scheduled for October 2021.","false","Biography information for Patrick Grady","Glasgow North","Patrick Grady","226695"
